    "description": "Waifu Crush is a PvEvP match 3 game with a strong strategy element with many special items called Charms.<br>You join the Super M3 Tournament's world where you meet and challenge all the Legendary Grandmasters to prove yourself!<br>You fight and defeat AI girls to earn charm then use these charms creating your strategy and challenge other players via PvP feature.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>HuniePop-like match 3 puzzle game with indirect matching mechanic (freely to move token in column and row)<br></li><li>Charms system that allow to build your match 3 puzzle battle more strategy<br></li><li>PvE system that allow to fight with smart AI girl<br></li><li>PvP system that allow you duel with other player<br></li><li>Proving yourself by get high much as you can in the ranked PvP mode</li></ul>",
